"avg_npc_180#1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾天你們不要到這裡來了。快回去。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌手。", "name": "安妮塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_180#1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不要拽我的裙子。你不是那麼小的小孩子了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是想說......我想好我要什麼了。我想聽你唱歌。", "name": "安妮塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_180#2"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為......我不知道什麼是歌。我聽到你在夢裡哼了。但我聽不懂。", "name": "安妮塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_180#2"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌手，你答應了？這是不是就是約定？", "name": "安妮塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_180#3"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算是吧。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（皺眉）", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的琴。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？是啊，歌手，你的琴去哪裡了？", "name": "安妮塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_180#2"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我回去找。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我幫你一起找。", "name": "安妮塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_180#2"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是不是說，你願意跟我一起回去啦？太、太好了！", "name": "安妮塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_180#3"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_180#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的......值得這麼高興？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes